name: Sideswiped
overview: Birthday girl Olivia realizes she’s been “swiping left on life.” Feeling like she’s been missing out, Olivia goes on a swiping rampage and vows to date all 252 of her matches.

episodes.name: Matching Up
episodes.overview: Single and miserable at 35, Olivia plunges into the world of online dating, with the help of Mary, her recently widowed mom, and Jayne, her younger, married sister.

episodes.name: Baby Steps
episodes.overview: Olivia dates a younger guy, causing Jayne to evaluate just how much spontaneity is in her own marriage.

episodes.name: Deal Breakers
episodes.overview: Olivia meets a great guy, but he may have a major deal breaker. Meanwhile, Jayne decides to try one of Olivia's new sex tips on Jim.

episodes.name: The Rock Star
episodes.overview: Olivia dates one of Jim's geeky co-workers, Mary goes out with a celebrity, and Jayne has serious mother-in-law issues.

episodes.name: The Ex
episodes.overview: Olivia runs into her ex, hoping to rekindle the past, while Mary tries to land a job— her first ever.

episodes.name: Bad Eggs
episodes.overview: Olivia sees a doctor about freezing her eggs, while Jayne secretly chats with one of Olivia's matches… as Olivia.

episodes.name: For A Nickel I Will
episodes.overview: Olivia starts to date Charlie, Jayne's Tinder crush, so Jayne throws a dinner party to meet him.
